---
title:  The world changes quickly. People do not.
subtitle: "People do not"
author: "Tanaka Chingonzo"
date:   2017-09-15 22:47:12
---
---
Wherever you are, seek beauty there. Find it in yourself. In everything, and in the nothingness that touches you when you fail. It touches your skin: it does not touch you. Your soul cannot be touched. It cannot be torn or damaged. But even then, it is constantly healing.
